## Data Flow

### Phase 1: Build (static, runs once)

```
catalog-page.md (or legacy docs/README.md)
  -> copy-component-docs.ts reads content
  -> extractTitleFromContent() pulls H1 heading
  -> stripProviderPrefix() removes provider name from title
  -> generateSlug() converts title to URL-friendly slug
  -> generateFrontmatter() creates YAML frontmatter with stripped title
  -> rewriteCatalogLinks() rewrites internal /docs/catalog/ links to use slugs
  -> writeComponentDoc() writes index.md with frontmatter + content
  -> writePresets() copies preset YAML/MD pairs
  -> generateProviderIndex() writes provider index with PROVIDER_DISPLAY_NAMES title
```

### Phase 2: Structure Generation (static, runs once after Phase 1)

```
site/public/docs/ (built markdown files with frontmatter)
  -> generate-docs-structure.ts scans all directories
  -> reads YAML frontmatter from each index.md
  -> builds hierarchical DocItem[] tree
  -> writes docs-structure.json
```

### Phase 3: Runtime (client-side)

```
docs-structure.json
  -> DocsSidebar.tsx loads and renders sidebar tree
     - provider directories: ProviderIcon + item.title
     - component items: per-component icon + item.title
  -> page.tsx extractCatalogProviders() reads provider metadata
     - passes to CatalogProviderGrid
     - grid renders provider.title (from frontmatter, not .toUpperCase())
```

